    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304830/extras/2fe303e6f35e06c33711400cce5cf524.poster.avif?t=1735604292\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304830/extras/2fe303e6f35e06c33711400cce5cf524.webm?t=1735604292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304830/extras/2fe303e6f35e06c33711400cce5cf524.mp4?t=1735604292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to play <strong>Outside</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out there, you'll find all sorts of people that need help!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect items and costumes while exploring the caves and</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >forests of this little town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Familiar characters from other worlds are sure to help you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax and giggle at the silly predicaments this place has to offer and enjoy these outdoors!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Objective</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outside is an open world game where your goal is to help the curious assortment of characters; collecting costumes and items to complete various quests scattered around the town. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 Collectible Costumes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Possible Endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic Original Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easter Eggs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304830/extras/5836e8a1ba1eb1b37d2b465b2aed8971.gif?t=1735604292\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304830/extras/5836e8a1ba1eb1b37d2b465b2aed8971.poster.avif?t=1735604292\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=209 /></picture></span></p>",
